WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.692
Hey everyone, I’m David from IFAL, the English learning app, and I’m happy you’re here.

2
00:00:06.692 --> 00:00:13.923
Today, I’ll share five interesting news stories and help you learn some English along the way.

3
00:00:13.923 --> 00:00:21.231
So sit back, pour yourself a coffee—maybe a strong one like we Israelis love—and let’s dive in.

4
00:00:21.231 --> 00:00:22.731
1.

5
00:00:22.731 --> 00:00:25.192
Five New TV Series for July 2026

6
00:00:25.192 --> 00:00:29.115
I read that July 2026 is full of exciting TV shows.

7
00:00:29.115 --> 00:00:41.500
There’s a new season of “Mahubrim” and another of “El Atzmi,” plus the final chapter of “Haderech LaBayta.” Even “HaPishtu’a” is coming to TV for the first time.

8
00:00:41.500 --> 00:00:53.115
If you like action, there’s a thriller with the star of “The Queen’s Gambit,” and a wild road-trip series about two women running away from everything.

9
00:00:53.115 --> 00:00:56.654
All these series will **premiere** this month.

10
00:00:56.654 --> 00:01:01.192
Premiere means the first official show of a season – בכורה.

11
00:01:01.192 --> 00:01:10.269
I know many of us watch on our phones during traffic jams on the Ayalon or when we’re in the army waiting for the bus.

12
00:01:10.269 --> 00:01:16.577
It’s fun to talk about these shows with friends over coffee or at the corner café.

13
00:01:16.577 --> 00:01:19.038
Which one would you watch first?

14
00:01:19.038 --> 00:01:20.538
2.

15
00:01:20.538 --> 00:01:22.923
Madonna’s Rare Interview on BBC

16
00:01:22.923 --> 00:01:28.615
Music legend Madonna sat down with Graham Norton in a special BBC program.

17
00:01:28.615 --> 00:01:35.923
It was filmed in the small club where she gave her very first gig in Britain over 40 years ago.

18
00:01:35.923 --> 00:01:45.308
In the interview, she talks about her childhood, the loss of her brother, and her relationship with her daughter, Lourdes.

19
00:01:45.308 --> 00:01:51.154
The program coincides with the **launch** of her new album “Confessions II.”

20
00:01:51.154 --> 00:01:55.538
Launch means to start or introduce something new – להשיק.

21
00:01:55.538 --> 00:02:01.923
I think it’s inspiring: a superstar returns to the same place where it all started.

22
00:02:01.923 --> 00:02:09.077
It reminds me of local bands that play in little clubs in Tel Aviv before they become famous.

23
00:02:09.077 --> 00:02:14.000
It shows that even big names come from small, humble beginnings.

24
00:02:14.000 --> 00:02:15.500
3.

25
00:02:15.500 --> 00:02:19.885
Netflix’s Nostalgic Remake of “Little House in the Negev”

26
00:02:19.885 --> 00:02:28.192
Next, Netflix is bringing back a classic Israeli show, “Little House in the Negev,” with a fresh **remake**.

27
00:02:28.192 --> 00:02:32.654
Remake means a new version of something old – עיבוד מחודש.

28
00:02:32.654 --> 00:02:38.269
The original story is about a family living in a remote desert community.

29
00:02:38.269 --> 00:02:48.577
The new version keeps the heart of the tale, because, as one actor said, the family and story are loved by so many people for so long.

30
00:02:48.577 --> 00:02:51.654
I feel nostalgic just thinking about it.

31
00:02:51.654 --> 00:02:57.500
When I was a kid, my grandparents in the south used to talk about that show.

32
00:02:57.500 --> 00:03:06.115
Now many young people can enjoy a modern take on it—maybe even while they’re splashing in the pool by the beach.

33
00:03:06.115 --> 00:03:07.615
4.

34
00:03:07.615 --> 00:03:10.462
Amazon Plans a Huge Bond Issue for AI

35
00:03:10.462 --> 00:03:17.231
In business news, Amazon is planning to raise at least $25 billion by selling **bonds**.

36
00:03:17.231 --> 00:03:22.615
A bond is a type of loan that a company sells to investors – אגרת חוב.

37
00:03:22.615 --> 00:03:28.154
They want this money to fund big investments in artificial intelligence.

38
00:03:28.154 --> 00:03:31.769
This is one of the largest bond offerings ever.

39
00:03:31.769 --> 00:03:36.154
It shows how important AI is becoming for big tech firms.

40
00:03:36.154 --> 00:03:43.000
In Israel, too, we see startups focusing on AI, from cyber security to self-driving cars.

41
00:03:43.000 --> 00:03:49.538
It’s exciting but also makes you think: what kinds of jobs will we have in ten years?

42
00:03:49.538 --> 00:03:51.038
5.

43
00:03:51.038 --> 00:03:54.885
Brazilian Flip-Flops Brand Rider Arrives in Israel

44
00:03:54.885 --> 00:04:02.346
Finally, a fun story for summer: the famous Brazilian flip-flops brand Rider is coming to Israel.

45
00:04:02.346 --> 00:04:10.038
The company got an **exclusive** license to import and sell these sandals only in the “Gali” stores.

46
00:04:10.038 --> 00:04:16.115
Exclusive means only one person or group has the right to do something – בלעדי.

47
00:04:16.115 --> 00:04:22.577
The collections will change every month and include styles for men, teens, and kids.

48
00:04:22.577 --> 00:04:25.269
Prices start at just 79.90 shekels.

49
00:04:25.269 --> 00:04:30.654
Oh, and flip-flops are the casual shoes you wear on hot days – כפכפים.

50
00:04:30.654 --> 00:04:39.115
I can already picture walking down Dizengoff Street in them, with an ice cream in hand, enjoying the sunshine.

51
00:04:39.115 --> 00:04:41.808
That’s it for today’s news roundup.

52
00:04:41.808 --> 00:04:52.500
I hope you found these stories interesting and that you learned a few new words: premiere, launch, remake, bond, exclusive, and flip-flops.

53
00:04:52.500 --> 00:04:55.423
Thanks for spending this time with me.

54
00:04:55.423 --> 00:04:59.577
I really enjoyed helping you learn some English today.

55
00:04:59.577 --> 00:05:04.885
Remember, with IFAL you get great lessons—only 20 shekels per lesson.

56
00:05:04.885 --> 00:05:06.385
See you next time!

